Full Description: PremierInterns.com aim to bring awareness to internships and make it more mainstream to the public. Internships are beneficial to both the employers and the interns due to their cost-effectiveness and necessary experience gained that is much needed to get hired on as a full-time employee. We want to bring visibility as well as availability to the masses and not limit it to certain demographic, geography or specific colleges and universities.

Description: ACRES ReServ is a public benefit corporation dedicated to elevating clinical research site quality, safety and productivity
Headquarters Regions: Washington DC Metro Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Alliance for Clinical Research Excellence and Safety (ACRES) and co-founders Greg Koski, Daniel O'Connor and Larry Kennedy created ACRES ReServ (ReServ) as a Delaware Public Benefit Corporation to provide concentrated, focused support for the tremendously successful ACRES Site Accreditation & Standards Initiative (SASI). ACRES in partnership with the British Standards Institution developed the first uniform global standard for clinical research sites and independent third-party accreditation. Accreditation promotes professionalism and enhances sustainability while reducing the cost and time required to effectively evaluate promising products. It also supports regulatory oversight and compliance while ensuring the promotion of responsible ethical conduct to make new, safe medicines available to patients more quickly and with improved outcomes. ACRES ReServ was created to commercialize the accreditation standard worldwide.  As a public benefit corporation, the ReServ directive serves ACRES mission while harnessing the power of entrepreneurial enterprise to deliver and support innovative clinical research site accreditation, operational and regulatory and compliance solutions. By operating as a for-profit business venture, ReServ’s charter is to promote and enhance the safety, quality and productivity of clinical research worldwide.

Description: Outsourced Legal Advisement: New York Quality - Suburban, Flat-Fee Pricing - 24/7/2 Service Guarantee
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: The motto of our firm is “We’ll Sleep When We’re Dead”; and along those lines we guarantee a 24/7/2 level of service (24-hours a day, 7 days a week, with response time to email/voicemail of no less than 2 hours).  Our commitment to those service levels are meant to be equal to or superior to what would be available from a full-time General Counsel employee and absolutely unobtainable from any outside counsel that our clients might otherwise choose to engage.  We only work on a quarterly, flat-fee basis that is meant to be priced at less than half what a full-time General Counsel employee would cost; so no one has to give a second thought to picking up the phone or emailing us to get something done, and our expense becomes a predictable-fixed cost rather than variable.  Most importantly, the General Counsel that we provide becomes an important member of our client's management team who completely understands their business, its challenges, human resource and strategic goals. We’ve often heard it said that perfection is unobtainable and that no one has ever met the perfect lawyer.  We refuse to accept that idea; we're more inclined toward the view of Aristotle who espoused that – and we paraphrase - pleasure in the job puts perfection in the work.
